Linux / macOSWindows PowerShell <pre><code>./pchain_client transaction submit --file &lt;PATH_TO_TRANSACTION_FILE&gt; --keypair-name &lt;KEYPAIR_NAME&gt;
</code></pre> <pre><code>./pchain_client transaction submit `
--file &lt;PATH_TO_TRANSACTION_FILE&gt; `
--keypair-name &lt;KEYPAIR_NAME&gt;
</code></pre> <p>After submitting the transaction to RPC successfully, you should receive a message that describes the content of the transaction. The transaction hash in the content will be useful later on when you want to check its status. Still, transactions may fail for various reasons. We suggest you test the transaction and estimate the gas used in the testnet.</p>
